Final Match Details

Botafogo 0-1 Atlético-MG
Date: December 19, 1971
Venue: Maracanã (Rio de Janeiro)
Attendance: 46 458
Referee: Armando Marques (SP)
Red Cards: Mura, Carlos Roberto (Botafogo)
Goal: Dario Maravilha 63'
BOTAFOGO: Wendell, Mura, Djalma Dias, Queirós, Waltencir; Carlos Roberto, Marcos Aurélio (Didinho); Careca (Tuca), 
          Zequinha, Jairzinho, Ney Oliveira. Coach: Paraguaio
ATLÉTICO: Renato, Humberto Monteiro, Grapete, Vantuir, Oldair; Vanderlei, Humberto Ramos; Ronaldo, Lola (Spencer), 
          Dario, Tião. Coach: Telê Santana

